  <p> 1.  A place to write the Situation or Task, then the Action and the Result. <br />
    Note Information describing the STAR/AR must include detail in the 5WH format:  Who, What, When, Where, Why, How.</p>
  <p>2.  The STAR/AR (redirector) follows after completing the above detail and should show the recommended alternate 'Action' and 'Result' that could have been followed.</p>
  <p>Once completed the form must be photocopied and a copy sent to the manager, a copy to Human Resources for the staff members file and the original given to the staff member.&nbsp;
